    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic balance of reliability and style, perfect for someone seeking a dependable daily driver that still turns heads. The exterior paint retains a beautiful gloss, showing only minor stone chips and light surface marks typical of careful road use. Inside, the cabin is remarkably clean and smoke-free; the bolsters on the seats are firm, and every button, dial, and digital display functions exactly as it should. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health, with a smooth-shifting transmission and a responsive engine that has benefited from regular, documented oil changes and preventative maintenance. It drives straight, brakes confidently, and offers a quiet, comfortable ride. This is an honest, well-maintained car that is ready for its next chapter without needing immediate investment.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
